{"tid":15640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【溝女王開班】德國調情高手 教年輕難民點樣追女","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:54:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56053431da3a1e0c16c2c1ae1dd4b5d88018e7ec","tid":15640,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1129 21:02<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161128/large/1480344342_f5b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161128%2Flarge%2F1480344342_f5b9.jpg&h=8044cc81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161128/large/1480344344_60df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161128%2Flarge%2F1480344344_60df.jpg&h=412a9ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生說：「神創造了你給我」、「我愛你，能否在你家睡覺？」老師隨即糾正稱：「你們在一起的首三個月都不要說你愛她，否則她們會跑掉，德國女孩不喜歡太『黐身』。」大家可能對這些師生對答大感奇怪，其實這是德國「溝女王」開班，教授敍利亞及伊拉克難民如何追求德國女性。<br />\n<br />\n27歲溫策爾（Horst Wenzel）是名副其實的調情高手，不但會在電視及電台「傳授功力」，亦會收費授課：單對單一天盛惠1,400歐元（1.1萬港元），如果一組人上課則收4,000歐元（3.2萬港元），至少有50萬人是他的網誌支持者，學習如何追求異性。<br />\n溫策爾今次免費向難民授課，是因過去2年逾百萬難民入境，大部份都是來自受戰火蹂躪的穆斯林國家，在處理兩性關係方面與德國普遍的方式截然不同，不少人亦不懂如何與德國女性溝通。溫策爾稱：「發展一段關係是融入的最佳方式，正是我開班的原因。」<br />\n上周他在多蒙特開班教導11名年青難民，包括如何搭訕、讚賞女性、首次約會要如何有創意並令對方留下深刻印象等。溫策爾又提醒學生，在德國就算是第一次約會，只要情到濃時，上床亦是普通不過的事。<br />\n24歲來自敍利亞的穆罕默德（Omar Mohammed），外型不俗，希望可以娶一位德國女子為妻，但他坦言因文化及宗教差異，不懂如何與德國女性接觸。他的夢想其實不難實現，因部份德國女性對中東男子特別有好感，又埋怨德國男人「喝太多啤酒、看太多足球及膚色太白」。<br />\n美聯社 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161129/55977670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161129%2F55977670&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1d3b84de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161129%2F55977670&h=3d007d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161129/55977670</a><br />\n #good2# 0    #bad# 1<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3a59f0b850bd8ffb867ac9eea33df4fb9bc71f00","tid":15640,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔撚識德文呀仆街"},{"pid":"662249032400e3d14d6427425267d2440aa1172d","tid":15640,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"洗撚溝咩，蛔直接姦架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1287701a25396fe8f24fad3a37a7c08ad1e09ec2","tid":15640,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ff2d2e22de73c64b8d9529dc4e233e8f216e8b","tid":15640,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚溝咩，蛔直接姦架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩呀 <br />\n強姦大國洗撚溝咩<br />\n去做gym 練大隻夠力咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127eb5cf9f55846fabd64bb106303d3af0bfe2fe","tid":15640,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"睇左d內文 覺得佢幫手排斥難民"},{"pid":"d03717494f31278fb3a7de6efb7000fa667633ab","tid":15640,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"呢條德奸黎....<br />\n人黎同我雞姦佢再拎去填海"},{"pid":"c0feee696ad8cc3883332045cdec0f5ba3d40f2f","tid":15640,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e8a851a1a25740313210fe2311cb41e4d2d8b","tid":15640,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢條德奸黎....<br />\n人黎同我雞姦佢再拎去填海</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc94700a7cae8855f7eedd230bfbee542d09578b","tid":15640,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"係德國西部住左一年，極少極少見到白人女仔會同中東人/黑人拍拖，支那妹食洋腸就好多"}]}